name: Cthugha (Tokyo Afterschool Summoners)
description:
A Dreambooth model trained on top of YiffAI 2.2.20 with 203 images of Cthugha from Tokyo Afterschool Summoners. Images were captioned with e621 tags without underscores or commas.

Positive Tags

Captions all began with:

  1. safe/questionable/explicit

  2. cthugha (tas)

  3. dragon

Most captions included:

  • anthro

  • male

  • solo

  • red body

Other tags included in captions:

  • headshot portrait

  • bust portrait

  • half-length portrait

  • three-quarter portrait

  • full-length portrait

  • low-angle view

  • high-angle view

  • side view

  • rear view

  • fully clothed

  • topless

  • bottomless

  • nude

  • penis

  • tentacles

  • torn clothing

The outfit in his first skin is tagged with "cthughajacket cropped jacket". His second is tagged with "cthughacoat coat".

Negative Tags

It seems to have trouble with his eyes. More than anything I use empty eyes in the negative prompt.
